Package: passport
Title: Manage Access Credentials with R
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Michele Stefano", "Altieri",
    email = "michelestefano.altieri@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Manage username and password for databases or web services
    in order to provide full access to external resources without exposing
    credential within the code.
